To use docker

1. Add your user to the `docker` group

```
usermod -aG docker <user>
```

2. Enable cgroup v2 by adding `cgroup_no_v1=all` to your kernel boot
parameters and reboot

3. (Optional) Configure user namespaces

```
echo <user>:100000:65536 > /etc/sub{u,g}id

cat > /etc/docker/daemon.json <<EOF
{
	...
 
	"userns-remap": "default"
}
EOF
```

